      "category": "class_policies",
      "content": "Students are encouraged to arrive 10–15 minutes before the start of class. For safety reasons, entry may be refused if you arrive more than 10 minutes after class has begun. Late arrivals who are not admitted are treated as no-shows and may forfeit the class credit.",
