      "category": "class_policies",
      "content": "Age ranges listed for kids and teens classes (e.g., 6–8 years) are guidelines to help place students in the most appropriate level. A 7-year-old may enroll in any class that includes ages 7 within the stated range. The studio reserves the right to recommend a different level if it better matches the student’s experience and maturity.",
      "is_active": true
    },
    {
      "id": "payment-and-refunds",
      "title": "Payments, Refunds & Credits",
      "category": "payments",
      "content": "All sales for single classes, class packs, and memberships are final and non-refundable once purchased. In cases of illness or injury, store credit may be offered at the studio’s discretion with a doctor’s note. Gift cards are treated as cash value and cannot be redeemed for cash.",
      "is_active": true
